	 <title>System.DayOfMonth</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This operator returns an Integer from 0 to 31 representing the day of
		  the month.</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select TableDee add { DateTime(2004,04,19).DayOfMonth() Date;</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>Date
----
19</programlisting> 
	 </example> 
